{"tid":1127243,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳展鵬晒肌輸畀伍允龍","createTime":"2019-04-27T03:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T06:11:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"45fae96c618ce0ae7b7092d1cc180f4bde31a3a4","tid":1127243,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:20:17.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】陳展鵬、陳山聰與伍允龍（Philip），昨日為新劇《唐人街》拍攝打鬥戲，三人更半裸晒肌肉，以Philip的八塊「朱古力」最搶眼，將陳展鵬比下去。Philip透露由劇集開拍已開始操肌，為了肌肉更突出，已「脫水」兩日。山聰則自言只「脫水」一日，不敢像Philip般搏命。他謂：「日前到泥涌一個沙灘拍打鬥戲，辛苦到想死呀！只可以不停漱口補充水分，拍完打戲終於可以食菠蘿油喇！」Philip聞言即高呼要吃叉燒飯。展鵬直言因忙湊B而沒時間操練，只能盡力而為，又試過山聰及Philip的方法，因體脂過低已見暈。<br />\n問到拍完後會否保持操肌？山聰表示一定會繼續；Philip則耍手擰頭，笑言要主力操手指肌肉，皆因要瘋狂打機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gyN8R5njAw_JKpekr0VbVA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/D02d_enp01p26270419.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FgyN8R5njAw_JKpekr0VbVA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2FD02d_enp01p26270419.jpg&h=fa330aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%B3%E5%B1%95%E9%B5%AC%E6%99%92%E8%82%8C%E8%BC%B8%E7%95%80%E4%BC%8D%E5%85%81%E9%BE%8D-221931528.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25B1%2595%25E9%25B5%25AC%25E6%2599%2592%25E8%2582%258C%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E7%2595%2580%25E4%25BC%258D%25E5%2585%2581%25E9%25BE%258D-221931528.html&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcsy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=bca6e0ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%B3%E5%B1%95%E9%B5%AC%E6%99%92%E8%82%8C%E8%BC%B8%E7%95%80%E4%BC%8D%E5%85%81%E9%BE%8D-221931528.html</a>"},{"pid":"6dcaba86693016ae19f911ae6cd820b579d57e7d","tid":1127243,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:23:51.000Z","msg":"飛左件亞視佬會好好多"},{"pid":"4d039b84e8e225dcf6c637c6b59deb6cd0bd7